data.description: Amazing two story Townhouse, in the lovely coveted Murphy Creek Subdivision .As you enter the home you will notice a spacious living area with high ceilings, beautiful kitchen with granite countertops , and 40 inch maple cabinets. 1/2 bath on the main level with an additional storage closet. The second floor has a laundry room in which washer and dryer are included . Nice work / desk on second floor landing area. Large primary bedroom with impressive vaulted ceilings, walk-in closet,and full bathroom. Second Bedroom also has vaulted ceilings, and walk-in, and full bathroom. There are three remote controlled ceilings fans. All appliances are to stay. Well sized two car garage, dry-walled, and two overhead storage racks. A 9x12 ft enclose patio, room for guest and a grill! Plenty of parking throughout the complex for guests. Just steps away for the Famous Murphy Creek Golf Course, community tennis courts, clubhouse, pool, and community park with a large picnic area for you and your family to enjoy. Conveniently located near E-470, DIA, I-70, DTC, Aurora, Southlands Shopping center, and Buckley Air Force Base.
